content.raw:
Just finished a first review. Things are looking good! It would be nice to test more of the API, ideally we'd have close to 100% test coverage for the `Actor` class.

I'm trying to find out why we haven't been getting new coverage reports on codecov, You can see the previous reports [here](https://codecov.io/bb/osrf/sdformat).
